dataprimeQuery.text:
source logs 
| filter $l.applicationname.inArray($p.application) 
| groupby $l.applicationname as Application, $m.timestamp / 10m agg count() as count

source logs 
| filter $l.applicationname.inArray($p.application)
| groupby $l.applicationname as Application, $m.timestamp/ $p.timeRange.suggestedInterval agg count() as count

source logs 
| filter $l.applicationname.inArray($p.application) | filter $m.severity.inArray($p.severity)
| groupby $l.applicationname as Application, $m.timestamp / $p.Bucket agg count() as count
